---
import "../styles/reset.css";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />

    <title>Selamat datang di web site milik Dika - sakitkepala.dev</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Halaman beranda sakitkepala.dev, web site personal milik Andika Priyotama"
    />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Almarai:wght@300;400;700;800&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="grid-layout">
      <nav class="navigation-menu">
        <a href="/dika" title="Ke halaman tentang Dika">/dika</a>
        <a href="/tulisan" title="Ke halaman tulisan blog">/tulisan</a>
        <a href="/karya" title="Ke halaman karya-karya projek">/karya</a>
      </nav>

      <header class="sakitkepala-heading">
        <div class="sakitkepala-heading-text">sakitkepala.dev</div>
      </header>

      <main class="content">
        <p>
          Hai. Web site saya ini baru <i>under construction</i> nih. Desainnya memang masih belum saya
          tentukan, tapi kontennya sudah ada, sih. Lihat-lihat dulu aja boleh. Terima kasih sudah mampir,
          yah.
        </p>
      </main>

      <footer class="footer">
        <a href="https://sakitkepala.dev" class="current-page" title="Alamat web sakitkepala.dev"
          >https://sakitkepala.dev</a
        >. Web site eksperimental oleh <a
          href="https://github.com/sakitkepala/sakitkepaladotdev"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          title="Repositori sakitkepaladotdev di Github">Andika Priyotama</a
        >.
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  body {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    font-family: "Almarai", "Inter", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
      Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Open Sans", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
  }

  html,
  body,
  .grid-layout {
    height: 100%;
  }

  :root {
    --grid-counts: 12;
    --grid-end: calc(var(--grid-counts) + 1);
  }

  .grid-layout {
    overflow-x: hidden;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-rows: auto max-content minmax(max-content, 1fr) auto;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
    row-gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 512px) {
    .grid-layout {
      grid-template-rows: auto 2fr 5fr auto;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(var(--grid-counts), minmax(40px, 1fr));
      gap: 0;
    }
  }

  .navigation-menu {
    grid-row: 1;
    grid-column: 1 / var(--grid-end);
    justify-self: end;

    margin: 1.5rem 2rem;

    display: flex;
    column-gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    flex-wrap: wrap;

    font-size: 2rem;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 512px) {
    .navigation-menu {
      marginblock: 1rem;
    }
  }

  a,
  a:visited {
    color: rgb(0, 0, 238);
  }

  a:hover,
  a.current-page {
    color: rgb(85, 26, 139);
  }

  a:active {
    color: rgb(238, 0, 0);
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 425px) {
    .navigation-menu {
      margin-inline: 1rem;
      align-items: baseline;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
  }

  .sakitkepala-heading {
    grid-row: 2;
    grid-column: 1 / var(--grid-end);
    overflow-x: scroll;
    height: max-content;
  }

  .sakitkepala-heading-text {
    margin-left: 2rem;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 11.5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 425px) {
    .sakitkepala-heading {
      overflow: visible;
    }

    .sakitkepala-heading-text {
      font-size: clamp(6rem, 1rem + 10vw, 180px);
    }
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
    .sakitkepala-heading {
      margin-inline: 1rem;
    }
  }

  .content {
    grid-row: 3;
    grid-column: 2 / var(--grid-end);
    margin-block: 1rem;
    margin-inline: 2rem;
    max-width: 28ch;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1rem + 4vw, 48px);
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
    .content {
      margin-inline: 0;
    }
  }

  .footer {
    grid-row: 4;
    grid-column: 1 / var(--grid-end);

    margin: 1.625rem 2rem;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
    .footer {
      margin: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
